WEBVTT

00:00.633 --> 00:02.701
<i>Previously on "zero hour"...</i>

00:02.703 --> 00:03.735
What am i looking at?

00:03.738 --> 00:05.270
A blueprint
for the son of god.

00:05.272 --> 00:06.405
They didn't want the cross.

00:06.407 --> 00:08.207
They wanted what was
inside of it.

00:08.209 --> 00:09.308
The blood of christ.

00:09.310 --> 00:10.509
Remember what happens

00:10.511 --> 00:12.077
Right before
the end of the world?

00:12.079 --> 00:14.346
Christ returns to earth.

00:14.348 --> 00:16.548
There is to be
no negotiation,

00:16.550 --> 00:18.617
Just death
and proof of death.

00:18.619 --> 00:21.387
Hank and laila die today.

00:21.389 --> 00:23.055
You'd fight for me?

00:23.057 --> 00:24.757
If anybody came at you,
i'd cut 'em in half.

00:24.759 --> 00:26.492
You do believe in god?

00:26.494 --> 00:30.529
I believe that there are things
beyond our comprehension.

00:30.531 --> 00:32.531
Is one of those things
a higher power?

00:32.533 --> 00:33.699
I don't know.

00:33.701 --> 00:36.235
I draw.
Helps me see things.

00:36.237 --> 00:38.704
Things i don't want
to forget.

00:38.706 --> 00:40.172
You really think
you can fix me?

00:40.174 --> 00:42.241
Your eyes will be sensitive
for a while.

00:42.243 --> 00:45.177
It didn't work.
Vision is a little bit off.

00:45.179 --> 00:47.179
You didn't come here

00:47.181 --> 00:48.514
To save me, did you,
laila?

00:51.218 --> 00:53.052
Beck, they're getting away.

00:53.054 --> 00:54.353
Come here, pretty one.

00:54.355 --> 00:56.555
Don't shoot!
He's got a hostage!

